SOURCE NOTES FOR THE DATA

The 102-compound v3 ground truth (data/v3_ground_truth.csv) is derived
from public sources:

  - DEA Schedule I–V listings (controlled-substance ground truth)
  - FDA-approved drug database (negative-control whitelist)
  - PubChem (canonical SMILES and identity resolution)

The original public sources remain under their respective terms. This
release contributes the curated benchmark composition, the parse-verified
SMILES set, and the ground-truth labeling decisions documented in the
companion manuscript.

The execution reports (reports/*) are original work product produced by
the deployed FAVES V4 service against this benchmark; they are subject to
this license in full.

